{
  "page": "A Game of Groans",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center; font-style: italic;\">A Game of Groans</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;text-align:center; font-style: italic; font-weight:bold;\">\nA Sonnet of Slush and Soot</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"A Game of Groans cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/86/A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg/300px-A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/86/A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg/450px-A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/86/A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg/600px-A_Game_of_Groans_cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\nGeorge R. R. Washington</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:United States\">United States</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:English language\">English</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\nCookbook</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\nSt. Martin's Griffin/<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Dunne_Books\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Thomas Dunne Books\">Thomas Dunne Books</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Released</th><td>\n27/3/2012</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Media Type</th><td>\nPrint (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paperback\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Paperback\">Paperback</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E-Book\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:E-Book\">E-Book</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">ISBN</th><td>\nISBN 1250011264</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>A Game of Groans</b></i>, is a parody book published by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Dunne_Books\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Thomas Dunne Books\">Thomas Dunne Books</a> and based on the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> fantasy series by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>. \nIn August 2011, Thomas Dunne Books announced that it had acquired the rights to <i>A Game of Groans</i>, a humorous take on Martin's best-selling novel, <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_notes\">References and notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Groans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n</div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template talk:AS